===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Kukui (Masters)}}
Kukui forms a [[sync pair]] with {{form|Lycanroc|Midday Form}} {{TP|Professor Kukui|Lycanroc}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. As the Masked Royal, Kukui forms a sync pair with {{TP|Professor Kukui|Incineroar}}. Kukui became a playable sync pair on January 30, 2020, with him appearing as the Masked Royal on June 17, 2021.

Kukui has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, [[Legendary Adventures]].  

